.TH StandardChessClocks 3 "Last change: 23 April 2004" "Release 0.5" "Ulm's Oberon System"
.SH NAME
StandardChessClocks \- standard implementation of \fIChessClocks(3)\fP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.Pg
PROCEDURE Create(VAR chessclock: ChessClocks.ChessClock;
                 pot: Shards.Pot;
                 nofplayers: SHORTINT;
                 timelimit: Times.Time);
.Pe
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I StandardChessClocks
provides a standard implementation of \fIChessClocks(3)\fP that is
based upon \fIClocks.system\fP.
.PP
.I Create
creates a new chess clock for \fInofplayers\fP players and the given
timelimit which must be a relative time measure. The lids that are passed to
\fIChessClocks.Start\fP, \fIChessClocks.Stop\fP,
and \fIChessClocks.Switch\fP will be checked against \fIpot\fP.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.Tb ChessClocks(3)
.Tp ChessClocks(3)
general interface for chess clocks
.Te
